01:18:34,346 --> 01:18:35,867
Yes, I'll go.

953
01:18:43,336 --> 01:18:45,305
Nisha! Nisha!

954
01:18:45,542 --> 01:18:48,511
Get up, child! Get ready, fast. Get up!

955
01:18:53,784 --> 01:18:54,844
What is this, mom?

956
01:18:56,999 --> 01:18:57,961
What a girl you are!

957
01:18:58,711 --> 01:18:59,250
Nisha!

958
01:18:59,594 --> 01:19:01,391
Get up, child.
Prem should be here any moment.

959
01:19:14,219 --> 01:19:15,125
Your slave is at your service!

960
01:19:15,991 --> 01:19:17,671
- Hi!
- Hi, Tuffy!

961
01:19:19,055 --> 01:19:20,172
Oh, God! I love her!

962
01:19:27,500 --> 01:19:28,133
Miss Nisha!

963
01:19:28,961 --> 01:19:30,679
- Thank you so much!
- Thank you?

964
01:19:31,187 --> 01:19:34,554
- For what?
- For waiting for me.

965
01:19:34,756 --> 01:19:37,100
I didn't wait for you.

966
01:19:37,358 --> 01:19:40,234
In that case, were you counting
stars in the day on the roof?

967
01:19:44,859 --> 01:19:49,867
People say, when a beautiful girl
lies; she looks more beautiful.

968
01:19:53,516 --> 01:19:54,586
MRS. CHOWDHURY: Have you come, son?

969
01:19:54,726 --> 01:19:55,273
Hello, auntie!

970
01:19:58,476 --> 01:20:00,312
How are you, auntie? Where's uncle?

971
01:20:00,442 --> 01:20:02,797
Good morning, son! A special snack.

972
01:20:04,640 --> 01:20:06,992
