979
01:20:25,169 --> 01:20:28,070
At least, taste it now.
Catch her hand. Taste it.

980
01:20:35,054 --> 01:20:38,351
Can I ask you something?
Why have I got these flowers, today?

981
01:20:38,804 --> 01:20:41,602
Basically, whenever we've
met, we've always fought.

982
01:20:42,281 --> 01:20:45,250
Flowers were the best way to
strengthen this acquaintance.

983
01:20:46,476 --> 01:20:50,882
Why did you ask me to forgive you
while leaving after the marriage?

984
01:20:51,045 --> 01:20:52,594
I was just trying to impress you.

985
01:20:54,719 --> 01:20:58,678
- If I tell you the fact, you will laugh.
- I won't. Tell me.

986
01:20:59,156 --> 01:21:02,312
It was that touching moment!
We were taking sister-in-law home.

987
01:21:02,508 --> 01:21:04,047
You were bidding her good bye.

988
01:21:04,312 --> 01:21:06,969
Thought to myself,
why not share some of your sorrows.

989
01:21:09,292 --> 01:21:12,586
Saw that, Tuffy?
A genuine man has no value!

990
01:21:14,062 --> 01:21:15,179
I wasn't laughing at you.

991
01:21:16,047 --> 01:21:18,648
Sometimes,
a human errs in judging a person.

992
01:21:19,281 --> 01:21:22,117
You aren't the type I thought you
were, when I first met you.

993
01:21:22,234 --> 01:21:23,133
Then...

994
01:21:23,831 --> 01:21:27,790
- ...how am I?
- I'll think of it at leisure and tell you.

995
01:21:28,344 --> 01:21:31,719
There's a surprise for
you in the back seat.

996
01:21:32,460 --> 01:21:33,117
Surprise?

997
01:21:33,327 --> 01:21:33,859
Have a look!

998
01:21:38,779 --> 01:21:39,576
Chocolates?!

999
01:21:39,836 --> 01:21:40,579
For you.

1000
01:21:41,516 --> 01:21:44,876
What's the matter, Tuffy?
Flowers first, then chocolates!

1001
01:21:45,774 --> 01:21:47,118
Is it some special day?

1002
01:21:47,422 --> 01:21:50,633
For the first time today, a girl is
sitting in the front seat of my car.

1003
01:21:53,541 --> 01:21:55,750
People say that this day
occurs in every person's life.

1004
01:21:56,376 --> 01:21:59,484
Today happens to be
that special day for me.

1005
01:22:03,037 --> 01:22:03,646
Miss Nisha!

1006
01:22:04,295 --> 01:22:04,756
Yes?

1007
01:22:04,898 --> 01:22:06,982
- What happened?
- Nothing.

1008
01:22:08,225 --> 01:22:11,670
I'm sharing my secrets with you
and you're with your comics.

1009
01:22:12,392 --> 01:22:14,360
It's not allowed to read
or write while travelling.

1010
01:22:14,646 --> 01:22:17,365
Travel should be full of songs and fun.
What do you say, Tuffy?

1011
01:22:18,155 --> 01:22:23,982
From the time I saw you singing on the
roof, I've become your fan.

1012
01:22:25,311 --> 01:22:27,467
You share some secrets, too.

1013
01:22:27,717 --> 01:22:29,834
- I won't tell anyone.
- Some other time.

1014
01:22:30,490 --> 01:22:32,599
- Why?
- I've a sore throat.

1015
01:22:33,975 --> 01:22:38,342
