01:27:24,751 --> 01:27:26,845
Big sister.... hi!

1052
01:27:28,064 --> 01:27:29,072
- Nisha!
- Hi!

1053
01:27:29,982 --> 01:27:31,200
Be careful!

1054
01:27:31,391 --> 01:27:32,602
Whoops!

1055
01:27:34,020 --> 01:27:35,505
- Hi, Chameli!
- Miss Nisha!

1056
01:27:35,530 --> 01:27:39,872
- Nisha child... welcome! May you live long!
