1058
01:27:41,974 --> 01:27:43,021
LALLOO: Good evening, Miss Nisha!

1059
01:27:43,168 --> 01:27:44,903
Oh, my!

1060
01:27:45,310 --> 01:27:46,638
Good evening, Mr. Lalloo!

1061
01:27:46,849 --> 01:27:48,435
Miss Nisha, welcome home!

1062
01:27:51,044 --> 01:27:53,622
KAILASHNATH: Daughter-in-law,
the in-laws have sent a lot of things.

1063
01:27:53,655 --> 01:27:56,528
- Mom has sent a letter for you.
- For me?

1064
01:27:56,553 --> 01:27:58,661
Wow, that's great!

1065
01:27:59,842 --> 01:28:03,435
'Respected in-law, I
hope, you all are fine.'

1066
01:28:03,731 --> 01:28:05,575
'I was very happy on seeing Prem today.'

1067
01:28:05,960 --> 01:28:08,841
'Do send Rajesh over here, for once.'

1068
01:28:09,786 --> 01:28:12,161
'The professor also
wants to say something.'

1069
01:28:12,278 --> 01:28:13,333
Oh, God!

1070
01:28:14,059 --> 01:28:17,091
'Well Kailashnath,
I've heard that these days you wear dhoti.'

1071
01:28:19,099 --> 01:28:21,583
'Every day, you listen to
daughter-in-law's rendition of Ramayana.'

1072
01:28:21,682 --> 01:28:25,536
'We haven't aged so much.
I'm sending a suit piece for you.'

1073
01:28:25,866 --> 01:28:28,723
'I have stitched a similar one.
You do the same.'

1074
01:28:29,036 --> 01:28:30,739
'On the joyous occasion
of the child's birth...

1075
01:28:30,833 --> 01:28:32,997
...both the grand fathers will
dance in similar outfits.'

1076
01:28:33,106 --> 01:28:33,668
Yes!

1077
01:28:33,919 --> 01:28:35,404
Take this, uncle.

1078
01:28:36,395 --> 01:28:39,544
Truly, daughter-in-law,
Nisha's coming has gladdened our hearts.

1079
01:28:39,982 --> 01:28:42,770
Tomorrow's function will be
very special now. - Right!

1080
01:28:46,665 --> 01:28:48,730
LALLOO: Welcome! Greetings!

1081
01:28:48,918 --> 01:28:49,918
WOMAN: Greetings!

1082
01:28:50,435 --> 01:28:53,419
I say, this place is decorated
in a different way today.

1083
01:28:53,444 --> 01:28:55,958
It has to be. It's our
daughter-in-law's first function.

1084
01:28:55,983 --> 01:28:57,208
- Right!
- Please, come.

1085
01:28:59,638 --> 01:29:00,919
Greetings! Please, come.

1086
01:29:01,732 --> 01:29:04,747
- Welcome, sister-in-law!
- Not sister-in-law, but my auntie.

1087
01:29:05,161 --> 01:29:06,419
Is that you, Bhagvanti?

1088
01:29:07,286 --> 01:29:10,208
- You look like Pretty Woman, today.

1089
01:29:10,692 --> 01:29:11,466
Naughty boy!

1090
01:29:12,630 --> 01:29:14,083
That's great, uncle.

1091
01:29:14,512 --> 01:29:14,776
Shut up!

1092
01:29:14,801 --> 01:29:17,512
Welcome, sister-in-law!
Welcome, elder brother.

1093
01:29:17,599 --> 01:29:19,356
All the guests have arrived.
Bhola has come, too.

1094
01:29:20,348 --> 01:29:22,161
Greetings, brother-in-law!
Greetings, Mr. Prem!

1095
01:29:22,186 --> 01:29:24,301
- When did you come, Mr. Bhola?
- He's here since the afternoon.

1096
01:29:24,326 --> 01:29:26,660
I have struck up a very good
friendship with your brother-in-law.

1097
01:29:26,685 --> 01:29:27,232
Come!

1098
01:29:27,257 --> 01:29:29,848
- Auntie... Oh, oh...
- What happened?

1099
01:29:30,206 --> 01:29:33,339
Wow, you are out to kill today!

1100
01:29:33,364 --> 01:29:34,145
- Really?
- Yes!

1101
01:29:34,216 --> 01:29:37,014
If not for this age difference... today...

1102
01:29:37,164 --> 01:29:38,618
Get lost, you shameless creature!

1103
01:29:38,665 --> 01:29:41,247
- Let go of my hand, you rascal!
- Auntie...

1104
01:29:41,272 --> 01:29:41,950
RITA: Prem!

1105
01:29:42,176 --> 01:29:43,403
Oh, God! Here she comes!

1106
01:29:46,360 --> 01:29:49,138
- Where did he go?
- Baby, who are these flowers for?

1107
01:29:49,163 --> 01:29:55,005
- They're for sister-in-law.
- Oh, the queen of the flowers has come.

1108
01:30:07,295 --> 01:30:09,795
WOMAN: You look very good today.
Come with us, please.

1109
01:30:09,820 --> 01:30:12,209
- Excuse me!
- Shakuntala!

1110
01:30:13,560 --> 01:30:14,791
- You?
- Yes.

1111
01:30:15,859 --> 01:30:18,906
Look, mister!
My name is Rita, not Shakuntala!

1112
01:30:18,931 --> 01:30:21,415
RITA... understand?

1113
01:30:21,750 --> 01:30:23,632
My knowledge of the English
language is a bit weak.

1114
01:30:23,657 --> 01:30:26,085
But whatever you just said,
I found it to be very sweet.

1115
01:30:27,827 --> 01:30:28,553
Stupid!

1116
01:30:30,312 --> 01:30:32,913
Brother, he has found his match.

1117
01:30:32,991 --> 01:30:34,077
