1131
01:31:15,088 --> 01:31:20,225
Doctor uncle, please repeat the
poetry that you just recited.

1132
01:31:20,655 --> 01:31:23,874
What's the matter, dear?
You seem very poetic today.

1133
01:31:24,226 --> 01:31:26,609
You never appreciated my poetry before.

1134
01:31:26,624 --> 01:31:29,296
Till today, he couldn't fathom
the depths of the poetry.

1135
01:31:29,343 --> 01:31:30,485
I mean, he didn't get it!

1136
01:31:30,510 --> 01:31:32,350
What do you say, Miss Nisha...
I mean, brother?

1137
01:31:32,663 --> 01:31:35,429
Doctor uncle, once more please!

1138
01:31:35,499 --> 01:31:36,335
Okay!

1139
01:31:36,444 --> 01:31:39,592
'These hours of waiting just
don't seem to get over.'

1140
01:31:39,693 --> 01:31:42,912
'The eyes are longing for
the love of life to appear!'

1141
01:31:43,226 --> 01:31:45,811
'The heart exclaimed,
the moment I saw the glamour of my love...

1142
01:31:48,445 --> 01:31:51,414
...who has brought her here
from the glory of heaven?!'

1143
01:31:51,827 --> 01:31:55,655
Wow! Very beautful!

1144
01:31:55,702 --> 01:31:58,523
