on here all the time?

1145
01:31:58,550 --> 01:32:00,444
No, we were just about to leave.

1146
01:32:00,530 --> 01:32:01,163
Let's go, doctor!

1147
01:32:01,608 --> 01:32:04,888
Your snacks are ready for
you, on the lawns outside.

1148
01:32:04,913 --> 01:32:07,022
