1149
01:32:07,140 --> 01:32:08,171
Come on, girls!

1150
01:32:11,031 --> 01:32:11,968
Shall I come, too?

1151
01:32:12,937 --> 01:32:15,155
Sorry, gents now allowed!

1152
01:32:20,835 --> 01:32:24,553
