1176
01:33:46,061 --> 01:33:46,788
Leave!

1177
01:33:50,171 --> 01:33:51,343
Get out, out!

1178
01:33:55,078 --> 01:33:57,398
Your problems are over.

1179
01:33:59,656 --> 01:34:02,617
Excuse me, excuse me!

1180
01:34:02,679 --> 01:34:04,289
What's happening?

1181
01:34:04,531 --> 01:34:06,710
You don't bother. You just carry on.

1182
01:34:07,031 --> 01:34:08,609
