1183
01:34:08,634 --> 01:34:09,218
What say, auntie?

1184
01:34:09,250 --> 01:34:11,070
Mine? Go right ahead.

1185
01:34:12,335 --> 01:34:14,507
What's this new problem?

1186
01:34:14,812 --> 01:34:19,781
